# LIBRERAS NECESARIAS
library(dplyr)

## Adjuntando el paquete: 'dplyr'
## The following objects are masked from 'package:stats':

library(ggplot2)
## Warning: package 'ggplot2' was built under R version 4.5.1
library(scales)
## Warning: package 'scales' was built under R version 4.5.1
library(DT)
## Warning: package 'DT' was built under R version 4.5.1
# --- 1. Eliminar NA y seleccionar top 10 ms frecuentes ---
top_10_facility <- datos %>%
  filter(!is.na(Facility.Type)) %>%
  count(Facility.Type, sort = TRUE) %>%
  slice_max(n = 10, order_by = n) %>%
  pull(Facility.Type)

# --- 2. Filtrar datos solo para el top 10 sin NA ---
datos_top10 <- datos %>%
  filter(!is.na(Facility.Type), Facility.Type %in% top_10_facility)

# --- 3. Reordenar niveles de factor para visualizacin ---
datos_top10$Facility.Type <- factor(datos_top10$Facility.Type, levels = top_10_facility)

# --- 4. Tabla de frecuencias con estadsticos ---
tabla_facility <- datos_top10 %>%
  count(Facility.Type, name = "Frecuencia") %>%
  arrange(desc(Frecuencia)) %>%
  mutate(
    Posicin = row_number(),
    Porcentaje = Frecuencia / sum(Frecuencia),
    Esperada = sum(Frecuencia) / n(),
    Chi2_Parcial = (Frecuencia - Esperada)^2 / Esperada,
    Prob_Esperada = Esperada / sum(Frecuencia),
    Etiqueta = paste0(round(Porcentaje * 100, 1), "%")
  )

# --- Modelo geomtrico (experimental vs terico) ---
p_geom <- tabla_facility$Frecuencia[1] / sum(tabla_facility$Frecuencia)
tabla_facility <- tabla_facility %>%
  mutate(
    Prob_Geom = dgeom(Posicin - 1, prob = p_geom),
    Freq_Geom = round(Prob_Geom * sum(Frecuencia)),
    Residuo_Geom = Frecuencia - Freq_Geom
  )

# --- 5. Tabla interactiva DT ---
DT::datatable(
  tabla_facility %>%
    mutate(
      Porcentaje = percent(Porcentaje, accuracy = 0.1),
      Prob_Esperada = percent(Prob_Esperada, accuracy = 0.1),
      Prob_Geom = percent(Prob_Geom, accuracy = 0.1),
      Chi2_Parcial = round(Chi2_Parcial, 3)
    ),
  options = list(
    pageLength = nrow(tabla_facility),
    autoWidth = TRUE,
    scrollX = TRUE,
    columnDefs = list(list(className = 'dt-center', targets = "_all")),
    initComplete = JS(
      "function(settings, json) {",
      "$(this.api().table().header()).css({'background-color': 'darkblue', 'color': 'white', 'font-weight': 'bold', 'font-family': 'Segoe UI'});",
      "}"
    ),
    rowCallback = JS(
      "function(row, data, index) {",
      "$(row).css({'font-family': 'Segoe UI', 'background-color': '#f9f9f9'});",
      "$('td', row).css({'text-align': 'center', 'padding': '6px'});",
      "}"
    ),
    dom = 'tip'
  ),
  caption = htmltools::tags$caption(
    style = 'caption-side: top; text-align: center; font-size:16px; font-weight: bold;',
    paste0("Tabla 5.1.2 Chi-cuadrado Facility.Type (Top 10)  X = ",
           round(sum(tabla_facility$Chi2_Parcial), 2), ", gl = ",
           nrow(tabla_facility) - 1, ", p  ",
           format.pval(pchisq(sum(tabla_facility$Chi2_Parcial), df = nrow(tabla_facility)-1, lower.tail = FALSE), digits = 3))
  ),
  class = 'stripe hover compact nowrap',
  rownames = FALSE
)
# --- 6. Grfico de Frecuencia Absoluta ---
ggplot(tabla_facility, aes(x = Facility.Type, y = Frecuencia, fill = Frecuencia)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 0.9) +
  geom_text(aes(label = Frecuencia), vjust = -0.5, size = 3.5) +
  scale_fill_gradient(low = "skyblue", high = "darkblue") +
  labs(
    title = "5.1.2 Frecuencia Absoluta de Facility.Type (Top 10)",
    x = "Tipo de Estacin",
    y = "Frecuencia Absoluta"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    panel.grid = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

# --- 7. Grfico de Frecuencia Relativa ---
ggplot(tabla_facility, aes(x = Facility.Type, y = Porcentaje, fill = Porcentaje)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 0.9) +
  geom_text(aes(label = Etiqueta), vjust = -0.5, size = 3.5) +
  scale_fill_gradient(low = "skyblue", high = "darkblue") +
  scale_y_continuous(labels = percent_format(accuracy = 1)) +
  labs(
    title = "5.1.2 Frecuencia Relativa de Facility.Type (Top 10)",
    x = "Tipo de Estacin",
    y = "Frecuencia Relativa"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    panel.grid = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

# --- 8. Grfico Comparacin Experimental vs Terico (Geomtrico) ---
ggplot(tabla_facility, aes(x = Facility.Type)) +
  geom_bar(aes(y = Frecuencia, fill = "Observada"), stat = "identity", width = 0.4, position = position_nudge(x = -0.2)) +
  geom_bar(aes(y = Freq_Geom, fill = "Terica"), stat = "identity", width = 0.4, position = position_nudge(x = 0.2)) +
  scale_fill_manual(name = "Distribucin", values = c("Observada" = "skyblue", "Terica" = "darkblue")) +
  labs(
    title = "5.1.2 Comparacin Frecuencia Observada vs Terica (Geomtrica)",
    x = "Tipo de Estacin",
    y = "Frecuencia"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1),
    legend.position = "top",
    panel.grid = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )

# --- 9. Correlacin entre Frecuencia Observada y Geomtrica ---
ggplot(tabla_facility, aes(x = Freq_Geom, y = Frecuencia)) +
  geom_point(color = "skyblue", size = 3) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE, color = "darkblue", linetype = "dashed") +
  labs(
    title = "5.1.2 Correlacin: Frecuencia Observada vs Terica (Geomtrica)",
    x = "Frecuencia Terica (Geomtrica)",
    y = "Frecuencia Observada"
  ) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "bold"),
    panel.grid = element_blank(),
    axis.line = element_line(color = "black")
  )
